  "texts": [
    "Further, as a proof of concept, we conducted a drug screening test using LEGOs derived from the additional iPSC cell line.",
    "Our findings mirrored those observed in the original cell line, with mTOR inhibitors demonstrating consistent efficacy across all three genotypes, CDK4/6 inhibitors exhibiting no discernible effect, and CDK1/2 inhibitors showing notable effectiveness (Supplementary Fig. 7i).",
    "Particularly, MEK1/2 inhibitors emerged as the most efficient in PTN organoids.",
    "Moreover, the drug identified through multi-omics analysis and prior drug screening, Lomitapide, exhibited favorable results in LEGOs derived from the new cell line (Supplementary Fig. 7i).",
    "Complete information on treated drugs and outcomes can be found in Supplementary Table 6."
  ],
